# Description:



#Prerequistes

Ubuntu 12.04 (Precise)

  Compiling (optional):

    $ sudo apt-get install nodejs npm
    $ sudo npm -g install coffee-script
    $ sudo npm -g install less
    $ make

  Running:

    $ sudo apt-get install python-setuptools python-pip
    $ sudo pip install tornado

OS X (10.8)

  Compiling (optional):

    Downlaod "Macintosh Installer" from http://nodejs.org/download/
    Install pkg

    $ sudo npm -g install coffee-script
    $ sudo npm -g install less
    $ make

  Running:

    $ sudo easy_install pip
    $ sudo pip install tornado

#Building

#Installation

#Usage

$ python vespa.py

Override settings from etc/server.ini by creating etc/server.ini.local
